skdetail:

Invocation Name: good deeds
Developer Terms of Use
des: Good Deeds allows you to sign petitions and contact your elected officials to advocate for issues you care about. Using just your voice you can engage in impactful advocacy quickly and effortlessly. No more online sign ups or looking for information about your elected officials. Good Deeds does it all for you. Go ahead and do a good deed today!
